===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|godbwye||lang=enm}}, contraction of {{term|God be with ye||lang=enm}}

===Pronunciation===
* {{enPR|go͝odbīʹ}}, {{IPA|/gʊdˈbaɪ/}}, {{SAMPA|/gUd"baI/}}
* {{audio|En-us-goodbye.ogg|Audio (US)}}
* {{rhymes|aɪ}}

===Interjection===
{{en-intj}}

# [[farewell]]; a formula used to another person or persons when the speaker or writer or the person addressed to is [[depart]]ing.

